  EffectDiscription_ENG: "[When Digivolving] For each card with [Hybrid] in its traits
    in this Digimon's digivolution cards, trash 1 digivolution card from the bottom
    of each of your opponent's Digimon. Then, for each Digimon your opponent has
    with no digivolution cards, \uFF1CDraw 2\uFF1E. (Draw 2 cards from your deck.)
    [On Deletion] You may play 1 blue level 4 or lower card with [Hybrid] in its
    traits from your hand without paying its memory cost."
